Lots of fine suspended matter- apparently from 4th of July boat traffic
Greenish cast to water surface- green color not observed when looking down over disc
Continued greenish cast to water surface- floating white powdery substance- possibly pollen
Lake water color is affected by some turbidity.
Last reading for 1993- need reporting cards for 1994.
Sunny- warm 60 degrees F- water very clear.
Water slightly hazy.  The water is yellowish brown.
Partly sunny- 53 degrees F @ 1400- 1.8" rain 10/12-10/26.  Last secchi reading for 1995.
Lake water no longer hazy but secchi depth still not normal.
Beautiful day- sunny- 74 degrees F- no wind.
Beautiful- sunny day.  Temperature 65 degrees.  Ice out 4/27/97.  Rain gauge reading from 4/19/97 to 5/26/97=3.30 inches.
Rain gauge reading from 5/27 to 6/18= 2.70 inches.
Rain gauge reading from 6/19/97 to 7/21/97=5.05 inches.
Rain gauge reading from 7/23/97 to 8/19/97 = 3.85 inches.
Sunday of Memorial Day (week after) lots of boat traffic.
Calm day- sun out- light traffic.
Slightly windy- sun out- light traffic.
Slightly windy- 3 days after 3 " of rain.
Really clear this spring - not much boat traffic today.
little windy - may have affected depth of reading
Lake seems clearer longer this summer - perfectly calm.
Lots of traffic yesterday - sun not bright.
Beautiful day ... some boat traffic on the lake yesterday
Beautiful Sunny Morning ... no boat traffic
100% cloudy - very windy - no boat traffic - 57 F air temp

column1: Did testing with Eddie Heath of Onterra

column2: very windy - partly sunny - hard to hold boat still - no boat traffic
partly cloudy - steady slight wind - air temp 60 - water murky - no boat traffic
air time 69 degrees- calm- cloudy- no boat traffic- high humidity- two loons swimming by us- Barb- my wife helped as usual
Air Temp 64 degrees - partly cloudy - rained the last two days - breezy so surface is hard to see through
Air Temp 73 degrees F - Hazy- very humid- steady breeze- no boat traffic
Windy- overcast misting at times.  Air temp 54 degrees
Sunny- clear sky- slight wind.  Air Temp 66.2 degrees

column1: a pair of loons on the lake this AM

column2: Temp 57 degrees - sunny and calm on lake - yesterday it rained most of the day.

Has been rainy for several days.  1.3 inches of rain last night.  Partly sunny - moderate wind - air temp 41.4 degrees  Am on my way to take the boat out for the year.  Saw a loon still on the lake on my way to take out the boat.
